featured knight fellow paddy hirsch knight garage knight garage knight talks about rss twitter featured knight fellow paddy hirsch by pam maples aug 12 2011 knight fellow paddy hirsch experimented with new approaches to telling stories and engaging news audiences during his year at stanford and began work on developing a digital archive of open source explainers to help people understand financial news but hirsch also explored what makes a happy productive workplace which led him to some contrary views about news media companies rush to make journalists do everything all of the time watch his short talk on this topic and learn more about hirsch at our new knight profile pages comments off posts by pam maples share on twitter facebook delicious digg reddit previous post next post comments are closed knightgarage stanford edu contact us john s knight fellowships knight garage powered by wordpress and jenny site admin
